<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" href="%PUBLIC_URL%/favicon.ico" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#000000" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="AHP (Analytic Hierarchy Process) 의사결정 지원 시스템"
    />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="%PUBLIC_URL%/logo192.png" />
    <link rel="manifest" href="%PUBLIC_URL%/manifest.json" />
    <title>AHP System</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Cache-Control" content="no-cache, no-store, must-revalidate" />
    <meta http-equiv="Pragma" content="no-cache" />
    <meta http-equiv="Expires" content="0" />
    
    <!-- Apply default blue theme immediately -->
    <style>
      :root {
        /* Default Gold Theme - Applied immediately to prevent flash */
        --accent-primary: #C8A968;
        --accent-secondary: #A98C4B;
        --accent-light: #E5D5AA;
        --accent-hover: #B59A4D;
        --accent-focus: rgba(200, 169, 104, 0.35);
        --accent-rgb: 200, 169, 104;
        
        /* Legacy compatibility */
        --gold-primary: #C8A968;
        --gold-secondary: #A98C4B;
        --gold-light: #E5D5AA;
        
        /* Interactive colors */
        --interactive-primary: #C8A968;
        --interactive-primary-hover: #B59A4D;
        --interactive-primary-light: #E5D5AA;
        --interactive-secondary: #A98C4B;
        
        /* Component colors */
        --favorite-bg: #E5D5AA;
        --favorite-border: #C8A968;
        --favorite-text: #A98C4B;
        --favorite-hover-bg: #C8A968;
        
        /* Focus and effects */
        --shadow-focus: rgba(200, 169, 104, 0.35);
        --focus: rgba(200, 169, 104, 0.35);
        --ring: #C8A968;
        --border-focus: #C8A968;
        
        /* Shadows */
        --shadow-accent: 0 4px 20px rgba(200, 169, 104, 0.25);
        --shadow-gold: 0 4px 20px rgba(200, 169, 104, 0.25);
        
        /* AHP specific */
        --ahp-primary: #C8A968;
        
        /* Layout and spacing */
        --header-height: 72px;
        --sidebar-width: 280px;
        --container-max-width: 1880px;
        --space-4: 1rem;
        --space-6: 1.5rem;
        --space-8: 2rem;
        --radius-md: 8px;
        --shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        --shadow-md: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        
        /* Background and text colors */
        --bg-primary: #ffffff;
        --bg-secondary: #f9fafb;
        --bg-elevated: #f3f4f6;
        --text-primary: #1f2937;
        --text-secondary: #6b7280;
        --text-muted: #9ca3af;
        --border-light: #e5e7eb;
        --border-medium: #d1d5db;
      }
      
      /* Ensure proper box-sizing and reset */
      *, *::before, *::after {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        background-color: var(--bg-primary);
      }
      
      /* Ensure proper React root styling */
      #root {
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      /* Ensure root takes full space immediately */
      #root {
        min-height: 100vh;
        background-color: #ffffff;
      }
    </style>

    <!-- GitHub Pages SPA 라우팅 스크립트 -->
    <script type="text/javascript">
      // Single Page Apps for GitHub Pages
      // Convert redirected URLs back to proper HashRouter format
      (function(l) {
        if (l.search && l.search[1] === '/' ) {
          var path = l.search.slice(1).split('&')[0];
          window.history.replaceState(null, null,
              l.pathname + '#' + path + l.hash
          );
        }
      }(window.location))
    </script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <noscript>
      <div style="text-align: center; padding: 50px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
        <h1>AHP System</h1>
        <p>You need to enable JavaScript to run this app.</p>
        <p>이 앱을 실행하려면 JavaScript를 활성화해야 합니다.</p>
        <p>Please enable JavaScript in your browser settings and refresh the page.</p>
      </div>
    </noscript>
    <div id="root"></div>
  </body>
</html>